      "content": "it's not even about needing to feel \"grounded\" or whatever. it's just that everything feels so pointless. like, if i'm just a ghost in this city, then why am i working so hard to pretend i'm part of it? it would honestly be so much quieter if i just... stopped. if i wasn't here, the world wouldn't even skip a beat. it feels like it would just be a relief to not have to carry all this weight anymore.",
